oai_dc:dc.dc:description: From the petrol extract of stem bark of Garuga pinnata a new euphane triterpene alcohol was isolated. The structure elucidation employing spectroscopic methods (UV, IR, H-1 NMR, C-13 NMR, 2D NMR) revealed this as 13alpha,14beta,17alpha-lanosta-7,24-diene-1beta,3beta-diol.
